T1  - Appropriability Mechanisms and the Platform Partnership Decision: Evidence from Enterprise Software
AU  - Huang, Peng
AU  - Ceccagnoli, Marco
AU  - Forman, Chris
AU  - Wu, D. J.
Y1  - 2012/10/24
PY  - 2012
DA  - 2013/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.1120.1618
